{
  "2189310": {
    "name": "Letters to Arralla",
    "steam_appid": 2189310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/7576d0906465dc02320e687410b47bc3.avif?t=1766014614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras_big/7576d0906465dc02320e687410b47bc3.avif?t=1766014614 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as a turnip with a big juicy bum delivering mail to a cast of colourful characters on the sunny island of Arralla!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/31945e4b300184f3872bdc6be0888176.avif?t=1766014614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras_big/31945e4b300184f3872bdc6be0888176.avif?t=1766014614 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best part of delivering mail? You can open every single letter and look through everyone’s business! Whilst in the real world this is a crime, on Arralla Isle it’s perfectly acceptable, and even encouraged!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/f7a282fda82066d13b4accfa8efaf0d7.avif?t=1766014614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras_big/f7a282fda82066d13b4accfa8efaf0d7.avif?t=1766014614 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the Arralla Isle Deliberry service, you'll have to solve where each letter goes through pictograms drawn on each envelope - and they're not always obvious! &gt;:)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/65282b356e26b26966e39731485c6678.avif?t=1766014614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras_big/65282b356e26b26966e39731485c6678.avif?t=1766014614 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn of the island residents’ interpersonal problems through reading their mail - they will need your help to resolve them! Meet big booty cutie fruits like grouchy glassblowers, silly scientists, and deliver seriously creepy letters to an ominous house on a hill…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/b84dc0bbd4477cee29151e99e756a301.avif?t=1766014614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras_big/b84dc0bbd4477cee29151e99e756a301.avif?t=1766014614 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On Arralla Isle, there’s no rush. The pace is slow, like a lazy summer day, so you can relax while you play. Exploration is a treat in this beautiful Australian landscape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/e66c25ed25aaf6de2551aa8ca778cf7f.avif?t=1766014614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras_big/e66c25ed25aaf6de2551aa8ca778cf7f.avif?t=1766014614 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snap photos, kick over chessboard pieces, read about Arralla Isle’s history, throw stuff, discover secrets. The island is your oyster. You can even call your mum!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s plenty to do as a mail delivery turnip on Arralla Isle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189310/extras/293b7d9cab2c60c9010cfe9ed441d91c.avif?t=1766014614\" width=610 height=75 /></span></p>",
